<name>BRAKE</name>
<section id="1002J_S0010" variety="S0010">
<name>BRAKE CONTROL</name>
<ttl id="1002J_S0010_72Z6O_T00AN" variety="T00AN">
<name>VEHICLE STABILITY CONTROL SYSTEM (for ADVICS Made)</name>
<para id="RM000000XHK00BX" category="D" type-id="3001B" name-id="BC02G-10" from="200601">
<name>HOW TO PROCEED WITH TROUBLESHOOTING</name>
<subpara id="RM000000XHK00BX_z0" proc-id="RM0250U___00005L500000">
<content5 releasenbr="2">
<atten4>
<ptxt>The intelligent tester can be used at steps 3, 7, and 10.</ptxt>
</atten4>
<descript-diag>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>VEHICLE BROUGHT TO WORKSHOP</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>CUSTOMER PROBLEM ANALYSIS</testtitle>
<test1>
<ptxt>Interview the customer and confirm the trouble (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UZ100YX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>CHECK DTC AND FREEZE FRAME DATA</testtitle>
<test1>
<ptxt>Check and record a DTC and Freeze Frame Data.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Clear the DTC and Freeze Frame Data (See page <xref label="Seep02" href="RM000000XHV009X"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Reconfirm the DTC.</ptxt>
<test2>
<ptxt>Reconfirm the DTC based on the recorded DTC and Freeze Frame Data (See page <xref label="Seep03" href="RM000000XHV009X"/> for DTC Check/Clear, and <xref label="Seep05" href="RM000000XHY009X"/> for Freeze Frame Data).</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>If any of the DTCs U0100/65, U0123/62, U0124/95, and U0126/63 is output together with a CAN communication DTC, first check the appropriate sensor for a momentary open circuit (See page <xref label="Seep04" href="RM000000XHS00JX"/>).</ptxt>
</atten4>
<spec>
<title>Result</title>
<table pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="4.96in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="2.12in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>DTC is output</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>A</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>DTC is not output (Problem symptom does not occur)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>B</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>DTC is not output (Problem symptom occurs)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>C</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</test2>
</test1>
<results>
<result>B</result>
<action-ci-right>GO TO STEP 5</action-ci-right>
<result>C</result>
<action-ci-right>GO TO STEP 6</action-ci-right>
<result-ci-down>A</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>DIAGNOSTIC TROUBLE CODE CHART</testtitle>
<test1>
<ptxt>Proceed to Diagnostic Trouble Code Chart (See page <xref label="Seep06" href="RM000000XHU00AX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
<action-ci-fin>GO TO STEP 7</action-ci-fin>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>SYMPTOM SIMULATION</testtitle>
<test1>
<ptxt>Proceed to Diagnosis System (See page <xref label="Seep07" href="RM000000XHP009X"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>PROBLEM SYMPTOMS TABLE</testtitle>
<test1>
<ptxt>Proceed to Problem Symptoms Table (See page <xref label="Seep08" href="RM000000XHN009X"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>CIRCUIT INSPECTION</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>IDENTIFICATION OF PROBLEM</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>REPAIR OR REPLACEMENT</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
<descript-testgroup>
<testtitle>CONFIRMATION TEST</testtitle>
<results>
<result-ci-down>NEXT</result-ci-down>
<action-ci-fin>END</action-ci-fin>
</results>
</descript-testgroup>
</descript-diag>
</content5>
